{"title":"写在艾芜前辈的灵前","authors":["杨牧"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":1,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"写在艾芜前辈的灵前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨牧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭你，是哭一段道路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藤萝和险嶂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交织着，有泥泞溅满"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"榛莽中的那方穹庐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漂泊年年漂泊年年，流浪者啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里是寒？哪里是暑？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭你，是哭一本巨书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜月，松风，子规啼就"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一部血与肉的构筑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横读是海；竖读是焰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读不尽你苦难中的大生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读不尽你傲岸的清骨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭你，是哭一个婴儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芬芳，赤亮，清丽如初"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纯粹的洁净"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纯粹的明澈，纯粹得使"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"污秽因你而显得丑陋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贪欲因你而显得平庸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伪饰因你而显得卑俗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭你，是哭一种植物"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是艾，是蒿，是杉，是竹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一切关于生命的葳蕤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切关于草木的延续"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荣了又枯，枯了又荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界静静地躺卧着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有泥土在，便方兴未艾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有春风长随便永无荒芜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾——老——啊！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}